Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:10.78,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:19.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:31.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:37.89,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and the others who infiltrated \Nthe Eye of the Midnight Sun's base
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.43,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,continued to dominate the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:44.19,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Mereoleona tried to finish Raia off, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:45.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We can understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:49.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we're basically the same as them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They're mad because something \Nprecious to them was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:55.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A free kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:57.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,where everyone can acknowledge \Neach other and smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:01:00.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of kingdom I want to create
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:01.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,when I become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.55,italics,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,What a fool,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:06.37,italics,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,blurting out something so overambitious \Nwithout any hesitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:09.88,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,He's actually serious about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:15.13,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,There used to be a guy who \Nsaid the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:22.19,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,If all humans were like you two, then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:24.65,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:28.48,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,There's no stopping this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.21,0:01:35.78,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And around the same time, Licht... \Nno, Patry's true motive was revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:38.54,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Patry was once betrayed by the humans
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:41.62,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and witnessed the massacre\Nof many of his elven friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:47.08,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In order to bring back his friends, \Nhe had been acting as Licht this entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:51.83,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,The humans betrayed someone precious \Nto me. They betrayed all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:52.75,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:56.38,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This time, we'll destroy the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:02.87,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Humans, you shall serve as the\Nfoundation of the resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:05.27,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:07.94,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:30.79,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(299,1)}The Black Bulls Captain\Nvs\Nthe Crimson Wild Rose
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:50.75,main,Ril,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I have the \Nprofile just right yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:52.63,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:55.50,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We should have no problems \Ndefeating these insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:59.26,main,Ril,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so where's your boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.91,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:05.26,main,Ril,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, tell me. I'm dying to paint right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.35,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Master Licht is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.47,main,Ril,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what? What, what, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:31.04,main,Ril,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even do anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:43.09,main,Ril,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.85,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:55.38,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I wonder what's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.92,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}A Village Out in the Boonies: Hage
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:32.06,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,The demon's skull...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:37.47,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry. It'll be okay, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:40.06,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:42.38,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Even if something dangerous \Nwere to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:45.78,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,the Clover Kingdom has the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:49.28,italics,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... Yuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.78,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Town in the Common Realm: Nean
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.88,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,It's nighttime, but it looks \Nlike the sun's about to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:00.29,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, there were swords of \Nlight coming from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.75,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is \Ngoing on in this kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:17.31,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,What... is... that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:21.29,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This seems different from \Nthe swords of light earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:25.79,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,That light is like the light of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:28.82,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess this isn't the \Ntime to talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:33.08,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Is this another attack by \Nthe Eye of the Midnight Sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:40.46,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,It disappeared... but our \Nfriendship will never fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.13,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Gauche?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:46.88,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:49.12,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:50.59,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:54.47,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,It's... shining... really... bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:06.32,main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,M-Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.83,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Things keep happening one after \Nanother. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:28.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.89,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,What is this light?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.30,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.15,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? Huh, wait, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:58.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on with you now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You just started shining outta nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:09.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're done with that,\Nyou better explain what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.61,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:15.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:19.14,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,The era of the humans has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:29.15,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's the matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.90,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:36.16,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno... Hamon... Klaus...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:42.41,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Do not talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:48.17,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You are not one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:51.92,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Begone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:54.42,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Begone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:56.43,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Begone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:08:59.18,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Begone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:01.68,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Begone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.03,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Begone, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:19.75,main,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the time for revenge has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:30.74,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That light just now... wasn't an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:32.42,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So what the hell was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:35.14,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I feel strong magic throughout the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:39.68,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This ki... Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.76,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.99,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:46.14,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We must contact all the \NMagic Knights in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:51.61,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So you two finally showed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:08.21,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but why the hell are you all \Nshiny and attacking our comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:11.02,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Marx! Old Man Owen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:16.93,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we aren't the \Nmen you knew anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:24.94,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, we were destroyed by \Nthe humans of this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:26.47,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,We are elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:27.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Elves?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:32.16,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,This time, we'll be destroying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:35.48,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you did to us, we will \Ndestroy every last one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:39.29,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this sounds like it's \Ngoing to be a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:43.30,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The guy did say that once they \Ncollected all the magic stones,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:46.50,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,they'd be reborn into their true \Nforms and obtain enormous power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:51.75,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So the ones who were reborn aren't the \Nguys in the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:56.34,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You'll be put out \Nof your misery soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.68,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Marx's magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:04.62,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If any of these hit me, I'll lose \Nmy memory of what just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:09.60,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And now the jerk's speed \Nand range have skyrocketed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:23.54,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And Old Man Owen's healing \Nmagic also skyrocketed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:29.16,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,except now the healing's so powerful,\Nit'll bust a hole in my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:36.00,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be finished if either one of \Nthem manages to hit me. Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:40.76,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who that corpse is,\Nbut is it precious to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:50.52,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter who they are. \NAll humans are sinners and deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:52.19,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.41,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,If it's that precious to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:58.19,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,how about I rip it to shreds \Nright in front of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:07.28,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare make those two \Nsay shit like that ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:13.92,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,You're just going to be easier \Nto hit if you leap right at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.88,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Memory Magic: Torment Canceller!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Black Hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.88,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Dark Cloaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Lightless Blade Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:28.57,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.77,italics,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,This human's movements...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.27,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Cloaked Lightless Blunt Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:43.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You two can take a little nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:49.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,See, I swore to a man you both \Nrespected that I'd protect this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.37,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:13:00.00,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,These two don't even use battle magic, \Nand they were this much trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.51,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Red roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.07,main,Char,0000,0000,0000,,My comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:16.02,main,Char,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you let your guard down,\N considering you just woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:21.90,main,Char,0000,0000,0000,,Rest a while within my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:32.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's damn nice of you. \NIt's not like you, though, Spiny Prickly Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:37.18,main,Char,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, but you \Nseem quite skilled for a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.37,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:53.97,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There are powerful spells \Ngoing off everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:57.17,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is it another attack on the royal capital?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:01.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Get the hell outta here, you dumbasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:05.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys don't survive, \NI'll murder you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.87,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do much about the \Ndestruction to the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:17.91,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the citizens survive, \Nthe kingdom won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:21.23,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But if more of these things \Nkeep sprouting up everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:23.38,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,we might just get wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:28.82,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The scent from the roses is \Ncloaking the Prickly Queen's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:31.18,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:33.64,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:36.35,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I was always really badass \Nat playing hide-and-seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:39.07,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Cloaked Dimension Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:43.02,main,Char,0000,0000,0000,,You have impressive instincts for a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:48.43,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't instinct. \NI distinctly felt your ki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:49.53,main,Char,0000,0000,0000,,Ki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.87,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Three cheers for ki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:58.40,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The way she moves and her ki \Nare definitely Charlotte's,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.31,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but her magic combat tactics are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:03.17,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to her normal \Nmidrange attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.51,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,she's using roses that scramble \Nmagic with their scent
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:08.29,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,and a variety of close-range attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:11.13,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, she's not \Nleaving any openings now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:14.89,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Knocking her out with the blunt edge of \Nmy sword will be nearly impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:21.17,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I heard her roses turned blue when \Nshe got hit with that curse as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:24.17,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:26.98,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The curse upon the House \Nof Roselei has activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:37.91,flashbackitalics,Char,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:03.56,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's the big idea, you jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:07.07,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You flung the pasta soup \NI was eating everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:15.01,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,On missions, you're as cool as a cucumber \Nand always raring to go. So what gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:19.41,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I like tough girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:25.00,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But it probably wouldn't hurt to ask\Nsomeone for help once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:34.26,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Our Magic Knights Squads are full \Nof strong people you can rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:40.60,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but apparently \Nthe curse was broken back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:44.62,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, because of the curse,\Nher roses remained blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:50.44,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But an elf's in there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:54.11,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Did turning into something that's not \Nhuman kill off the lingering effects, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:58.49,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what Charlotte Roselei's \Nbriar magic was supposed to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:01.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You used the power of the curse
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:04.81,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,to make yourself stronger \Nthrough sheer grit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.88,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And now some other woman's \Nusing your magic perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:12.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty lame, Prickly Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:15.62,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.47,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:22.47,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:29.26,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,B-Back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:33.25,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,When you attacked us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:35.89,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:41.08,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,That was some kind of mistake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:44.58,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.35,main,Char,0000,0000,0000,,Stop acting so familiar with me, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:50.84,main,Char,0000,0000,0000,,I only have a younger brother. \NI have no younger sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:52.96,main,sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:58.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,She's basically being controlled by \Nsome kind of spell. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:00.39,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Black Bulls' captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:02.69,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deal with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:03.80,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:05.73,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But you showed up at a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:07.88,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:10.73,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Take this and get to someplace safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:13.69,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't take any requests from men!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:17.11,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, now's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.81,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:22.63,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hero in there. \NBe extra careful with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:23.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:26.62,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave my sis with any guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you dumbass! Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.85,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,How can I leave my sis and run off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:34.63,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring Sis back to her senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:39.25,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Magic: Divided—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:47.50,italics,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sis's magic is really dense here. \NIt's preventing me from using my magic well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.99,italics,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls' captain was \Ndoing all that in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:56.95,italics,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even fight properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:18:59.01,italics,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.82,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only alive now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:09.04,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,because Sis saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:13.54,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wake Sis up, even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:17.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:21.55,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission right now is \Nto protect and to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.91,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:25.72,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:31.23,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But you need to survive for \Nher sake, too, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:39.95,flashback,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone near \Nmy Sis! Especially men!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:44.11,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:49.00,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Save the Blue Rose Knights' captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:51.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me! Now get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:55.40,main,Char,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot run now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.09,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Who said I was gonna run?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:00.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Black Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:03.38,main,yami,0000,0000,0000,,Your subordinate is crying, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:06.86,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you letting \Nthem control you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:09.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're not that weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:11.68,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:19.10,main,Char,0000,0000,0000,,You have my respect. You are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:26.41,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That magic sure is insane. \NMy Black Hole can't absorb all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:28.85,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If she fires that off cleanly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:33.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,it'll blow away half this town, and we'll\N be dealing with a bunch of dead people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:38.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Tch! You've always had my respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:43.38,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So... I'll use everything I've \Ngot to take you back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:52.10,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:52.10,main,Char,0000,0000,0000,,Briar Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.56,main,Char,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson Vine Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:57.27,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Cloaked Dimension Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:15.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Luck? Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:19.67,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Golden magic... How beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:23.67,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Such menacing magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:26.24,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as Vetto and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:28.75,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that magic coming from you two?
