Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:09.35,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:13.91,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Noelle, the Beautiful Little\N Royal Girl of the "Na" Column
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:13.39,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle, the Beautiful Little \NRoyal Girl of the "Na" Column.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:15.39,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Languish (naeru).
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:17.50,sign_33427_257_Weaken__Naeru_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Languish\N{\fs20}(Naeru)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:17.50,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Gloomy gloom... I have no energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:18.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Stew (nieru).
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:21.75,sign_33427_257_Weaken__Naeru_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Stew\N{\fs20}(Nieru)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:21.75,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, hot, hot! You're stewing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:25.50,sign_33427_257_Weaken__Naeru_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sew\N{\fs20}(Nueru)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.27,0:23:23.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Sew (nueru).
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:25.50,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, I sewed this really well. Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:27.01,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Nails (neiru).
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:30.22,sign_33427_257_Weaken__Naeru_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Nails\N{\fs20}(Neiru)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.01,0:23:30.22,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isn't this one a bit of a stretch?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:32.50,main,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle (Noeru)!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.50,0:23:35.62,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Look at my grand appearance! \NBut what else did you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:37.45,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm royalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:42.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the?! The Eye of the Midnight Sun\N guy started shining outta nowhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:44.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and now he's super strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.05,0:23:45.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Rill?!
